    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age. The engine and transmission are currently functional, but you should expect some minor oil leaks and a suspension that feels a bit loose. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and some paint fading on the hood, while the interior shows significant wear on the driver's seat and carpets. It is a solid choice for someone looking for affordable transportation who doesn't mind performing some upcoming maintenance.",
