    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in style with this fantastic find! This car is in good condition and has been well-maintained, offering a smooth and reliable driving experience that you can truly depend on. It's the perfect choice for anyone looking for a comfortable and solid vehicle that\u2019s ready for its next adventure!",
