    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly a showroom-quality specimen that has been meticulously maintained. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and there are no dings, scratches, or imperfections to be found. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine state, with leather upholstery that looks and feels brand new and all electronic components functioning perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, offering a smooth and powerful driving experience as if it just rolled off the assembly line.",
      "price": 49000.0,
